"I'm going to be somewhere," he said. "How about that? We'll see. It's OK. I've got good options." ... Tigers LHP Darin Downs (left shoulder soreness) will make a rehab appearance Sunday for Triple-A Toledo. His return to Detroit after that isn't automatic. ... RHP Mike Adams, on Philadelphia's disabled list since June 21 with multiple right shoulder muscle tears, will have surgery on his shoulder next week that will put him out of action for at least the remainder of the season. He appeared in 28 games for Philadelphia this season, going 1-4 with a 3.96 ERA out of the bullpen.
